>Description:
Within the editor, there seems be a intermittant problem when copying sections of code.  It's as if the copying process doesn't "take".  In other words, I highlight the code, select Edit-Copy (or use Ctrl-C) to send it to the clipboard.  When I paste, I either get nothing or I get the leftovers of a previous copy attempt.  

The problem is very minor and difficult to make repeat.  But, it has happened enough times that I'm sure it's not just a erroneous keystroke on my part.

Otherwise, Scheme is working very happily on my Windows 98 platform.  :-)

Chana
