 Gee, I hate it when I answer my own questions.  It was my fault.  *sigh*
 When the text is grey-highlighted from matching parenthesis, it "looks"
 highlighted, but is not.  So, therefore the copy command does no good until
 you really highlight it.
 
 Sorry to trouble you.
